<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Congratulations on Your Course Purchase!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .order-container {
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 30px;
      width: 500px; /* Increased width */
      text-align: center;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #28a745;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      color: #666;
    }

    .order-info {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .thanks-message {
      color: #28a745;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .congrats-message {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .enjoy-message {
      font-style: italic;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #666;
    }

    .about-platform {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .team-info {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .order-table {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .order-table th, .order-table td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 12px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .order-table th {
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
    }

    .subtotal, .total {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="order-container">
    <h2>Congratulations on Your Course Purchase!</h2>
    <p class="congrats-message">Great choice! You're on your way to exciting new knowledge and skills.</p>

    <p class="order-info">
      <span>Order ID: <%= orderId %></span>
      <span>Order Date: <%= orderDate %></span>
    </p>

    <table class="order-table">
      <tr>
        <th>Course Name</th>
        <td><%= courseName %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Quantity</th>
        <td><%= quantity %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Order Cost</th>
        <td>$<%= orderCost.toFixed(2) %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Subtotal</th>
        <td>$<%= (quantity * orderCost).toFixed(2) %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Total</th>
        <td>$<%= (quantity * orderCost).toFixed(2) %></td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p class="thanks-message">Thank you for choosing Team LMS for your learning journey!</p>
    <p class="enjoy-message">Enjoy exploring the world of knowledge with us!</p>

    <div class="about-platform">
      <p>Team LMS is committed to providing a seamless and engaging learning experience. Our platform is designed to empower learners like you with high-quality courses, interactive content, and a supportive community.</p>
    </div>

    <p class="team-info">- The Team LMS</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
